msgstr "这样就会显示费用的 :guilabel:`客户发票草稿`。然后，就可以像往常一样完成发票开具流程。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst-1
msgid ""
"Sample customer invoice for an expense generated from a sales order in Odoo "
"Sales."
